// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1041 — Mass File Rename (thegentlemen)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: 51346043-d27f-5bc3-87aa-1419851b1421

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
